{"about_the_game":"A kidnapping on the streets of Shibuya brings together a hot-blooded detective, hard-hitting journalist, former gang leader, the head researcher of a big pharma manufacturer and a part-timer stuck in cat costume for a series of events each more unexpected and outrageous than the last. Can they\u2014or the city itself\u2014make it through the day?<br><br><strong>Game Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Real Actors and Locations<br>428: Shibuya Scrambleuses a mix of still photography and live action footage for a cinematic gaming experience that pulls you on a whirlwind tour of downtown Tokyo.<br></li><li>Tangled Fates<br>An innocent choice by one character can have disastrous consequences for another. Unravel the narrative threads, discover how they tie together and use the JUMP system to move between scenarios as five stories run in parallel.<br><br></li><li>Easter Egg Hunt<br>Sometimes the wrong decision can lead to the right outcome, or at least an amusing game over. With over 50 endings, multiple bonus modes and extra scenarios, there\u2019s more to the city than there seems.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/648580/extras/428_esrb_small2.jpg?t=1715700496\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Honorary S.O.S. Member","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/648580/636625c6953049013ae58275c85a878a3b75544a.jpg"},{"name":"The Worst is Over","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/648580/d392ffe8772a2f15f5a958da30d5faf19c00d920.jpg"},{"name":"The Solitary Serpent ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/648580/3c5946b52b3cc96a4380e2872b0602887f29ee1b.jpg"},{"name":"Final Curtain","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/648580/d392ffe8772a2f15f5a958da30d5faf19c00d920.jpg"},{"name":"The Three R's","path":"https://cdn